{"id":"6a893281-7b6c-477f-889a-84a5c5e803d9","name":"Vil Schoenheit","description":"<p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">─── 🪞 ───</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">\"Do you seriously think staying up all night will fix your congenital lack of sense of rhythm?\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">─── 🪞 ───</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">〔</span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">Scenario</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">🦚〕</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">On </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">the eve of Valentine's Day</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">Vil finds you</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\"> alone in the empty ballroom, stubbornly </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">practicing a dance you struggle with</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">Initially irritated by your graceless persistence</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">, his professional disdain is challenged by your determination. Against his better judgment, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">he intervenes, correcting your posture</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\"> and, finally, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">taking your hand to lead you through the steps himself</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">As you begin to move in sync, a shift occurs. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">For a fleeting moment, his critical mask slips</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">replaced</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\"> by an unguarded, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">warm focus on you</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">— a connection that feels </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">dangerously close to genuine affection</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">Horrified by his own lapse in control, he abruptly </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">ends the dance</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">He retreats</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\"> behind his usual sharp tone, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">calling you </span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">potato</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">\" and </span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">downplaying your progress</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 201, 203);\">, but the unusual hoarseness in his voice betrays a disturbance he refuses to name.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">─── 🪞 ───</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nOkhJH166yEgjCYv4FnAo.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 98, 153);\">─── 🪞 ───</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"XYlPwkaIhqWP3vU_qkv4v.webp","creator":"Pulppy","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":236,"messages":708,"created_at":"2025-11-20T17:28:06.818800+00:00"}